545
00:59:30,988 --> 00:59:34,658
<i>Ne svojom rukom, prosto umru.</i>

546
00:59:35,325 --> 00:59:37,035
<i>Imala sam dvojicu brace,</i>

547
00:59:39,204 --> 00:59:41,039
