- Ovo je bilo sjajno.

638
01:10:21,972 --> 01:10:23,932
Stvarno divna propoved oce.
Hvala.

639
01:10:24,057 --> 01:10:27,978
- Mike.
- Emily.

640
01:10:30,355 --> 01:10:34,526
Nisu ludi, Mike. Njeni roditelji.

641
01:10:34,651 --> 01:10:36,111
U pravu su što se nje tice.

642
01:10:36,236 --> 01:10:39,490
